'''巴吉拉奥一世''' ({{bd|1700年|8月18日|1740年|4月28日|}}) 是印度[[馬拉塔帝國|馬拉塔帝國]]的一名将军。他是帝国第四任皇帝{{tsl|en|Chhatrapati Shahu||沙胡}}的{{tsl|en|Peshwa||佩什瓦}}（首相）。他的任期是从1720年到1740年他去世。他也被称为巴吉拉奥·巴奥（Bajirao Ballal）和图里（Thorale，在[[马拉地语|马拉地语]]中为老者的称呼）.<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ez4wAQAAIAAJ|title=The Chitpavans: social ascendancy of a creative minority in Maharashtra, 1818-1918|publisher=Shubhi|year=2008|isbn=978-81-8290-132-2|page=82|author=Sandhya Gokhale}}</ref>

巴吉拉奥的功绩在于扩张了马拉地帝国的疆域而有功，尤其是在帝国北部。当他死后二十年，帝国领域在他儿子Balaji Baji Rao当政时期到达顶峰。巴吉拉奥为认为是{{tsl|en|Bhat family|派普家族}}九位佩什瓦中最为有影响的一位.<sup class="noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style="white-space:nowrap;" contenteditable="false">[''<span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources. (January 2016)">citation needed</span>'']</sup>

在他短暂的20年军队生涯中，巴吉拉奥从未输过一场战斗。据英军军官伯纳德蒙哥马利记载，巴吉拉奥是“印度有史以来最好的骑兵将军”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/news/column/why-bajirao-is-indias-greatest-cavalry-general/20151223.htm |title=Why Bajirao is India's greatest cavalry general |access-date=2016-05-04 |archive-date=2017-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908094845/http://www.rediff.com/news/column/why-bajirao-is-indias-greatest-cavalry-general/20151223.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
巴吉拉奥出生在{{tsl|en|Bhat family|派普家族}}中的{{tsl|en|Chitpavan|吉特巴万}}婆罗门世系。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EoRz7BEGyasC&pg=PT72|title=Indian Unrest|date=7 February 2012|publisher=tredition|isbn=978-3-8472-0599-9|page=72|author=Valentine, Sir Chirol}}</ref> 他的父亲{{tsl|en|Balaji Vishwanath|巴拉吉·维斯维纳斯}}是沙胡皇帝的第一任佩什瓦（首相），他的母亲是Radhabai. 巴吉拉奥有一个弟弟{{tsl|en|Chimaji Appa|奇玛吉·阿帕}}。<ref name="GSC_2005">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UkDi6rVbckoC&pg=PA19|title=Advance Study in the History of Modern India (Volume-1: 1707-1803)|date=1 January 2005|publisher=Lotus Press|isbn=978-81-89093-06-8|pages=19–28|author=G.S.Chhabra}}</ref>

巴吉拉奥从小跟随父亲南征北战，他父亲被{{tsl|en|Damaji Thorat|达玛吉·叟拉特}}囚禁，在交赎金之前他一直陪伴在他父亲身边。<ref name="GSC_2005">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UkDi6rVbckoC&pg=PA19|title=Advance Study in the History of Modern India (Volume-1: 1707-1803)|date=1 January 2005|publisher=Lotus Press|isbn=978-81-89093-06-8|pages=19–28|author=G.S.Chhabra}}</ref> 当他父亲1720年去世时，沙胡皇帝指派20岁的巴吉拉奥就任佩什瓦.<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=oAUdAAAAMAAJ|title=The Making of Modern India: From A. D. 1526 to the Present Day|publisher=Orient Longmans|year=1951|page=239|author=Shripad Rama Sharma}}</ref> 据说那时他就有了建立印度帝国（Hindu Pad Padshahi (Hindu Empire)）的想法,<ref name="PuriDas2003">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Y7fUHMEDAyEC&pg=PA212|title=A Comprehensive History of India: Comprehensive history of medieval India|date=1 December 2003|publisher=Sterling Publishers Pvt. Ltd|isbn=978-81-207-2508-9|pages=212|author1=B.N. Puri|author2=M.N. Das}}</ref>

